snippet.title: Pocket Mirror ~ GoldenerTraum  - Launch Date Announcement
snippet.description:
✦Steam Store Page
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1899060/Pocket_Mirror__GoldeneTraum

Pocket Mirror ~ GoldenerTraum is launching on Steam on May 19, Pre-Purchase Now!

In this remastered version, Pocket Mirror ~ GoldeneTraum brings back all the memorable contents of the original release with new visuals, additional features, a brand new ending and 2D animated sequences, extra content, and more.
